      <p class="xtime">25 Oct. 2005</p>
      <p class="xdes">Sam and Dean investigate an age-old urban legend known only as the Hook-Man, the spirit of a 19th century pastor with a twisted sense of morals that is unknowingly being used as an innocent girl's attack dog.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
